      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified+1\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/332567e2-a9be-11e4-953a-5254006e85c2).  Ran 7 tests.  No failures.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
