      "date": "2015-02-01 07:00:15.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.5/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/ceb25da8-a9de-11e4-8c6f-5254006e85c2).  Ran 18 tests.  No failures.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
